LovePop Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback























lovepop inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Home & Office Products
Sub-Industry: Home & Office Furnishings
Lovepop, Inc designs and develops greeting cards. The Company offers birthday, anniversary, wedding, seasonal, animals, boats, floral, spring, and special cards. Lovepop serves customers in the United States.




