LOVEPOP  Trademark Information
 LovePop, Inc.
(Based on Intent to Use) Custom design of paper products, namely, corporate cards for company anniversaries and other special events and milestones, calendars, and books; (Based on Use in Commerce) Custom design of paper products, namely, greeting cards, stationery, wedding stationery, corporate holiday cards, event invitations, wedding invitations, and decorative paper sculptures




Perfect for these industries

Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services





Words that describe this mark
based   intent   use   custom   design   paper   products         corporate   cards   company   anniversaries   special   events   milestones      calendars      books   based   use   commerce   custom   design   paper    
                                    




This is a brand page for the LOVEPOP trademark by LovePop, Inc. 
                                in Boston, MA, 02109.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this LOVEPOP trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner LovePop, Inc. of the LOVEPOP trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the LOVEPOP trademark.
                           






On Monday, May 09, 2016,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        LOVEPOP by 
                        LovePop, Inc., Boston, MA  02109.
                        The USPTO has given the LOVEPOP 
                        trademark serial  number of  87029430.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is FIRST EXTENSION - GRANTED.
                        The correspondent listed for LOVEPOP is 
                        
                        
                                            JOSHUA S. JARVIS, of 
                                            FOLEY HOAG LLP,  155 SEAPORT BLVD., BOSTON, MA 02210 
                                .
                            The LOVEPOP trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for LOVEPOP 
                            is (Based on Intent to Use) Custom design of paper products, namely, corporate cards for company anniversaries and other special events and milestones, calendars, and books; (Based on Use in Commerce) Custom design of paper products, namely, greeting cards, stationery, wedding stationery, corporate holiday cards, event invitations, wedding invitations, and decorative paper sculptures. 
                            





