corresponding Infringing Videos (together with the remaining two Infringing Designs, the 
“Infringing Works”) on its website www.paperpopcards.com. (Attached hereto as Exhibit 5 are 
print-outs from Paper Pop’s website showing each of the Infringing Works currently displayed 
there.)
