This is a brand page for the LOVEPOP trademark by JewelPop Inc 
                                in DARTMOUTH NS, , B2W6E2.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this LOVEPOP trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner JewelPop Inc of the LOVEPOP trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the LOVEPOP trademark.
                           






On Monday, September 12, 2011,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        LOVEPOP by 
                        JewelPop Inc, DARTMOUTH NS B2W6E2.
                        The USPTO has given the LOVEPOP 
                        trademark serial  number of  85419842.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for LOVEPOP is 
                        
                        
                                            Sara E. Hirshon of 
                                            VERRILL DANA, LLP,  PO BOX 586, PORTLAND, ME 04112-0586 
                                .
                            The LOVEPOP trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Jewelry Products 
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for LOVEPOP 
                            is Jewelry. 
                            





